I move to amend HB3435
Of the printed Bill
Page 1 Section 1 Lines 24
Of the Engrossed Bill
By inserting after the word "municipality" the following:
"unless otherwise provided for in the ballot proposal. Nothing in this
section shall prevent funds from being transferred to another department,
director, or agency within the municipality provided that the funds are
used for the project contained within the bond proposal."
